menu.description:
<a:gm7:960286343190175764> ‚ô¢ Medals

**Medals** will allow you to embed your cards rarity with either a `BRONZE`, `SILVER`, `GOLD`, or a extremely rare `PRISTINE` emblem. 

**Medals RNG Guide:**
> „Éª**Medal** RNG can fail and reward you with nothing.
> „ÉªYou can roll any **Medal** at once, you do not need to go in order of Bronze to Pristine.
> „ÉªWhen rolling a character with a **Medal** already applied, you will always attempt to increase the rarity of the **Medal**. This can fail.
> „ÉªYou can't downgrade a **Medal**, only upgrade.
> „ÉªRates for both obtaining and upgrading **Medals** are the same.

`DEMO:`
